reviewText: Great ! Wonderful for a trip to Malta

I was truly delighted to receive this DVD. It informed me of so much more historical and cultural detail then the textbook I use with my Graduate students in Tourism Geography.

I was delighted with the high quality of video production and historical detail and I will purchase more of these travelogues for use in my classes.

John Barnes
Bangkok,
Thailand
I enjoyed the total look of malta. I hope to visit this area. the buildings are marvelous inside and our.

All the history and information you could need for a trip to Malta and/or Gozo.  You will find these islands to be fascinating and full of historical things to explore, as well as modern day excitement.  Beautiful filming.
